Class ShippingDock

  • java.lang.Object
    • ShippingDock

  • class ShippingDock
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Elliot Lohr This class provides a blueprint for a Shipping Dock node, which receives orders from the ShippingSections and sends them to available DeliveryTrucks
